<taxonomicName box="[136,419,1988,2010]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="1" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pauwelsianum">Bulbophyllum pauwelsianum</taxonomicName>
<emphasis box="[424,534,1988,2009]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="27">differs from</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Lindl." authorityName="Lindl." box="[539,737,1988,2010]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Bulbophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="1" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="saltatorium">
B. saltatorium 
<emphasis box="[680,737,1988,2009]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="27">Lindl.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="27">
(1837: t. 1970) in the leaves being pendulous, linear, semiterete with upper surface concave and v-shaped, fleshy, not planar in transverse section; sepals ciliate with hairs more than 
<quantity box="[1215,1289,2024,2045]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="27" unit="mm" value="0.5">0.5 mm</quantity>
.
